cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.SY, cs.CE 

This paper deals with modeling and predicting the propagation of infectious diseases in large-scale metapopulations, which involves network inference and prediction using data and prior knowledge. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.SI (Social and Information Networks). Other likely sub-categories include cs.SD (Software Engineering), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science).
